Name: REENTRY
checklistText:
1. Retro Fire Green:
    a. Auto Retro switch - ARM
    b. Retro Jett Fuse - ON
    c. Emer Retro Jett Fuse - ON
2. Jett Retro Telelight goes green 60 seconds after Retro Fire signal.
3. Attitude Select - RE-ENTRY
4. Check correct attitude
5. Monitor attitude indicator until .05G
6. .05G Telelight - GREEN
7. Rate indicators indicate roll rate
